<template>
    <el-table
        :data="users"
        highlight-current-row
        v-loading="listLoading"
        @selection-change="selsChange"
        style="width: 100%;"
    >
        <el-row>
            <el-col :span="6">
                <el-table-column prop="name" label="编号"></el-table-column>
            </el-col>
        </el-row>
        <el-row>
            <el-col :span="6">
                <el-table-column
                    prop="description"
                    label="名称"
                ></el-table-column>
            </el-col>
        </el-row>
        <el-row>
            <el-col :span="6">
                <el-table-column prop="money" label="金额"></el-table-column>
            </el-col>
        </el-row>
        <el-row>
            <el-col :span="6">
                <el-table-column prop="edit" label="编辑"></el-table-column>
            </el-col>
        </el-row>
    </el-table>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            users: [
                {
                    name: "1",
                    description: "申恩",
                    money: "100000",
                    edit: "编辑"
                }
            ]
        };
    },
    methods: {},
    mounted() {},
    created() {}
};
</script>
